physical_appearance: The image shows twelve black-and-white negative of photographs. They are arranged in a four by three orientation. Each negative contains groups of people, either sitting down or standing up. Resolution of negatives are not high enough to identify more details.
sgcool_label_text: These plastic film negatives show 12 photographs of the committee members of the Peranakan Association in 2000.
title_text: Negatives of committee members of the Peranakan Association
subject_terms_2: Portrait photography Portraits, Group Peranakan Association, Singapore
